{"tid":1155434,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返新工","createTime":"2019-05-15T03:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T17:38:59.000Z","uid":42762,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2975267b9a8ac782563e47dedc5feac2844464","tid":1155434,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"上星期開始返新工，因為係轉行所以所有野對我嚟講都好新，因為帶我嘅同事成日唔係公司，變咗有唔少野要自己單獨處理，一做就出錯，錯到個人冇哂信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，上司問起野又成日答唔到佢想要嘅野，已經比佢話過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而家好驚同佢接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合呢幾年做野嘅經驗，發覺自已抗壓能力好差，一緊張個腦成日空白一片反應唔切，做野粗心大意唔得細心，適應力好差，返咗新工之後更明顯，跪求各位教下我可以點做先改善到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f7b5bf7a402acd9749a38ce1e415369534fe56","tid":1155434,"uid":122139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"由咩轉咩？"},{"pid":"731ec936d7e5f7e88d27769ab8b3f8ef7343ff7b","tid":1155434,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0f7b5bf7a402acd9749a38ce1e415369534fe56","tid":1155434,"uid":122139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"由咩轉咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2eefb47b83b58c80da0b9412e23fc3f47935ce","tid":1155434,"uid":122139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"731ec936d7e5f7e88d27769ab8b3f8ef7343ff7b","tid":1155434,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0f7b5bf7a402acd9749a38ce1e415369534fe56","tid":1155434,"uid":122139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"由咩轉咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:07:36.000Z"